# Summary
This documentation describes the Cordial destination integration with Amplitude, which enables syncing Amplitude cohorts to Cordial lists for targeted messaging and importing real-time customer data from Cordial to Amplitude for analysis. It details the setup process in both platforms and explains how cohort syncing works, including how list names are created and how contacts are added/removed.

